Never place ANTHROPIC_API_KEY in client-side code. Server routes only.
Currency is always PHP (₱), never USD.
Sticker tiers: 500=25, 1000=60, 3000=200, 5000=400, 10000=900.
Tier qualification is based on total pieces, not peso value.
All AI calls live in app/api/ only.
Do not add auth, payments, or a database.
Keep lib/tierEngine.ts a pure function with no framework imports so it stays unit-testable.
Nudge tone: warm, conversational Filipino business context, max two sentences.